    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Toys for small children where multiple activities are included in one toy. Each activity helps develop motor skills and hand-eye coordination. Examples of activities are a bead maze, shape sorter, musical toys, and abacus.  Activity toys can take multiple forms. Modern versions may be electronic.</Note_Text>
